28076BA6.Line7.84B74: If I’ve learned anything during my time here, it is that what we’re looking for and what we need are rarely the same thing.

5B76B812.Line21.84B74: Everything I’ve done has pulled me further from home, from the place I need to be.

7BA17FF7.Line35.84B74: This is how you choose to approach me?

B6DC9E59.Line25.BAE4: Lilith has entered the ancient city. With your blessing, I can pursue her.

D706C939.Line19.84B74: I once thought I could find an end to this war, but there has been no resolution. Only more pain.

DD9C3BA7.Line5.BAE4: I must traverse the black lake, and that cannot be done without your blessing.

F01812F6.Line16.84B74: Your kind are weak, and this world has been wasted on the crusades of the unworthy.

F56B3194.Line23.84B74: This world we made was born from the impossible. And yet, like its creators, it rots from the inside.
